Floyd Mayweather and Manny Pacquiao will fight in Las Vegas on May 2 . 
  Kenny Bayless will be the third man in the ring for the Fight of the Century . 
  Bayless has refereed previous fights involving Mayweather and Pacqiao . 
  Bob Arum says Bayless is the best referee in the world . 
  The pair will face off in the richest fight in history . 
 